title: Shaker Heights Beautiful 4 Bed 2 Bath 2 Family (19406 Winslow Rd.)
posting_body: Immaculate English Tudor on Prestigious (Historic Street) upper Winslow Rd. in Shaker Heights.
4 Bedroom/2 bath (upstairs unit 2nd and 3rd floor combined).

Some of the elegant and charming features include refinished hardwood floors, Wood burning Fireplace, sunroom, big leaded glass windows in living room, newer kitchen appliances with built in dishwasher and garbage disposal, washer/dryer, microwave oven, new boilers and windows.
This is not your average rental property.
This is the home I used to live in and I have gone the extra mile to make it extremely nice!
This is one of the nicest rental units on the street and in the neighborhood.
This includes: Two garage bays, AC window units, washer/dryer, stove, frig, dishwasher, microwave,  snow removal and very well manicured lawn service.
Excellent schools, close walk to the rapid and wonderful shopping within walking distance.
No pets, non smoking, no section 8, credit and background checks a must.
